high_descs: Move to the sink to the left of the fridge
Pick up fork from the counter
Clean the fork in the sink
Move to the table behind you
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned fork on the table.

high_descs: Turn left and head towards the sink.
Pick up the fork from the counter.
Turn around, look and turn back to the sink.
Wash the fork in the sink.
Pick up the fork, turn around and head to the table.
Set the fork on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the sink.
Pick up the fork from behind the sink.
Place the fork in the sink.
Wash the fork in the sink, then pick it up again.
Turn around and walk to the table in front of the window.
Place the fork on the left of the table in front of the loaf of bread.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed forked on a table.
